                         Charge Abe, discharge your brain, go party.

 *  Public install :    http://abe.lunaticpunk.com
    You can use it.
 *  Version :           0.2-Hilton
    Development/stable at the same time.

#####################################################################
##                            FEATURES                             ##
#####################################################################

Implemented:
 *  Categories: you can create categories (like folders) to put others
    categories or terms into.
 *  Terms: terms are definitions, write down your knowledge.
 *  Users: contents are linked with an user, you need one.

Incoming:
 *  categories/terms operations : move, copy
 *  tinyMCE integration
 *  different terms types
 *  some design things

